reviews.text:
You had me at butterscotch and ice cream. What I didn't expect was how much I'd love the banana in this. It rides the fine line between actual fruit and full blown candy banana, and does it extremely well. This is a fully flavored and utterly delicious vape. I've wrecked 30 mls of this stuff in a week, which usually only occurs when I can't wick properly. Fantastic stuff. For what was developed as a "Beginner's Week" flavor, just...good right out of the shake, and better after about 3 days. At a week, assuming it lives that long, it's just fantastic.&#xD;
&#xD;
Another banger from the brain trust!
